::Aerotaur::
    "I thank you for your insight.  Lead on.  But first can you walk or do I 
need to carry you?" he says to Dinotron.  He looks at Whistler, who is again 
unconscious, and without asking hoists him onto his back and turns to ask "I 
believe you were called Rust can you walk or do I need to carry you too?".

::Whistler::
    As he is lifted Whistler awakens enough to ask "Oooh.  Am I going for a 
ride?"  Before he slumps across Aerotaur's equine back.
